      "rationale": "At MRL 2, separate numerical solver error quantification beyond the code verification benchmark comparisons is not required. This factor is scoped out consistent with ASME V&V 40 Table 3 guidance for MRL 2."
    },
    {
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "factorType": "Use error",
