      "rationale": "The k-omega SST turbulence model was selected based on published benchmarking studies for rotating turbomachinery hemolysis simulations. Formal model-form uncertainty quantification is not required at MRL 2; the selection rationale is documented and accepted."
    },
    {
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
