    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors met or exceeded their required levels for MRL 2. The six factors not assessed were appropriately scoped out per ASME V&V 40 Table 3 guidance for a Class II device at MRL 2. The CFD hemolysis prediction model is accepted as credible for identifying worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for the FDA generic centrifugal blood pump under the conditions described in this assessment. Note: this package conforms to the Minimal profile; a structured Context of Use object has not been provided, and the intended-use scope is described only in the package narrative.",
